{"tid":807512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大研究指　吐露港附近地下水量　等同購入東江水量","createTime":"2018-09-05T14:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T11:15:52.000Z","uid":47714,"like":207,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"9b739b91859fa8206209ab542ea5ca35ea146c3b","tid":807512,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/14693/飲用水-水資源管理-地下水-14693/香港「缺水」的謎思之一\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F14693%2F%E9%A3%B2%E7%94%A8%E6%B0%B4-%E6%B0%B4%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86-%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%B0%B4-14693%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E7%BC%BA%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%8D%E7%9A%84%E8%AC%8E%E6%80%9D%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80&d=WCv99913tef268%2BYayrycPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d891fa59\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/14693/飲用水-水資源管理-地下水-14693/香港「缺水」的謎思之一</a><br />\n<br />\n【撰文：李妙梨】<br />\n<br />\n六七十年代，香港出現「制水」，更因為不夠水，當時大興土木興建了十七個水塘，成為香港重要的水資源，還有不少人常常提到最後方案：向中國購買東江水，解決「缺水問題」。可是<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>隨著科技進步，歐美國家及日本都在找尋或相繼應用新水源</strong></span>時，我們有沒有思考過：香港是不是仍要大量購買東江水呢？而我們的水資源管理系統又是否完善呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2017/07/360全景-郊野公園-大欖涌水塘-20170702114802_d57f_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2017%2F07%2F360%E5%85%A8%E6%99%AF-%E9%83%8A%E9%87%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92-%E5%A4%A7%E6%AC%96%E6%B6%8C%E6%B0%B4%E5%A1%98-20170702114802_d57f_large.png&h=e2c0c2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n360鏡頭下的大欖涌水塘。黃志全攝<br />\n<br />\n最近讀到不少有關水資源管理的資料，發現了<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>大部分「缺水」或將面對水資源短缺的國家或地區，都只是欠缺一套完善的水資源管理系統</strong></span>，而完善的水資源管理系統，並非一個食水安全法就足夠。以歐盟的水資源管理系統為例，就有一個water framework directive，所有會影響水質及保護不同水資源（如surface water（地面水）、groundwater（地下水）、bathing water（沙灘水及非飲用水）.....等）都在這條water framework directive 之下。此外，同農業發展、泥土、工業污染、污水處理⋯等，還有環保directives ，怎樣做好源頭減廢、化學物質應用及監管都在framework directive範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n再回到香港，莫說未有water framework directive，連最基本的食水安全法都欠奉，所以難怪<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2015 年時，新加坡學者Professor Asit K. Biswas 曾經指出香港的水資源管理方法相當落後</strong></span>，如果香港政府再不肯承認現有系統的弊病，很可能會出現比鉛水更嚴重的食水危機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2018/08/360全景-萬宜水庫-20180831043215_17bd_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F08%2F360%E5%85%A8%E6%99%AF-%E8%90%AC%E5%AE%9C%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB-20180831043215_17bd_large.png&h=f980aae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬宜水庫。黃志全攝<br />\n<br />\n而根據<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>2010 年的立法會文件，曾提及香港沒有可持續的地下水資源</strong></span>。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但在2015 年，就有一個香港大學的研究顯示，吐露港附近就可能有3850-6850 mcm 的地水儲備</strong></span>（<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>幾乎同我們每年購入的水量相若</strong></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果可以保護當地的生態環境，地下水是可以持續補充的</strong></span>）[1]，可惜當時未有再進一步研究，去探討水質⋯等。直到<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>2016 年，一位加拿大學者 Dr John Cherry 在香港硏究地下水水質[2]，發現香港不單沒有詳細的地下水研究，更發現香港地下水竟然已被污染，由於經費有限，未能找到污染的根源</strong></span>，只是推斷有兩個可能：1. 六、七十年代的工業污染。2. 香港的污水系統老化，污水滲漏入泥土，再污染地下水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>地下水一直是歐盟國家的重要水源</strong></span>，主要依賴地下水為食水的國家有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>奧地利、丹麥</strong></span>⋯等。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>德國及荷蘭都有七成食水是地下水</strong></span>，連<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>日本都有百分之十三的食水是地下水</strong></span>，所以如果香港可以改善地下水水質，更採用歐盟的水資源管理方法，地下水也有可能成為我們的重要水源儲備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2018/08/城門水塘-360全景-20180831043153_1139_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F08%2F%E5%9F%8E%E9%96%80%E6%B0%B4%E5%A1%98-360%E5%85%A8%E6%99%AF-20180831043153_1139_large.png&h=d62f7ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n城門水塘。黃志全攝<br />\n<br />\n在全球極端天氣影響下，為了未來仍然有足夠的食水，香港需要進行大規模的本地水資源硏究，同時還需要找出其他地下水源，更一定要找出地下水的污染源頭，避免及減低地下水污染，去淨化和保護這個珍貴的水資源。<br />\n<br />\n[1] Kwong, Hiu-tung鄺曉彤：Potential offshore groundwater reserves in Hong Kong by characterising submarine aquifer-aquitard systems (<a href=\"http://hub.hku.hk/handle/10722/228392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhub.hku.hk%2Fhandle%2F10722%2F228392&d=WCv99913tef268%2BYayrycPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a44b0a00\" target=\"_blank\">http://hub.hku.hk/handle/10722/228392</a>)<br />\n<br />\n[2]: SCMP：Check the groundwater: expert says city may be contaminated by leaked sewage and past industrial pollution (<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/health-environment/article/2003745/check-groundwater-expert-says-city-may-be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fhealth-environment%2Farticle%2F2003745%2Fcheck-groundwater-expert-says-city-may-be&d=WCv99913tef268%2BYayrycPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9db7573c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/health-environment/article/2003745/check-groundwater-expert-says-city-may-be</a>)"},{"pid":"655b0fa760a81cb1723571eea9645db1de4c7766","tid":807512,"uid":32171,"like":403,"dislike":5,"score":398,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"香港政府根本唔係買水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只不過係用一個藉口送錢俾支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cd0fda0c873c9d8de82c9b19b6d36a79be8df7","tid":807512,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95dbf73b92ed536e98470ea3d9269a914b8d10bc","tid":807512,"uid":3457,"like":152,"dislike":1,"score":151,"quote":{"pid":"655b0fa760a81cb1723571eea9645db1de4c7766","tid":807512,"uid":32171,"like":403,"dislike":5,"score":398,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"香港政府根本唔係買水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog